  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult patients ventilated more than 48 h

          -  Stable respiratory and hemodynamic conditions for SBT

          -  Consent of patients

          -  Arterial line

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe COBP

          -  Laryngeal dyspnea

          -  Tracheostomy

          -  Arrhythmia

          -  No echogenicity

          -  Paraplegia &gt;T8
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
